snippet.title: Danganronpa Weeping Rebellion  | Prologue 1/2 (Eng Sub)
snippet.description:
New cast, new environments and new ordeals that we're facing once more in another story for the fan community. This game was made by a French developer and there's  Voice Acting too 😀.  it was not translated by me, but it's still an enjoyable experience and I encourage anyone to give it a try!

💖Download Prologue : https://drive.google.com/file/d/1URGLxffuQnceGc_c0L2zRTzfj8VuHy60/view

🤎Support the channel! : https://ko-fi.com/zephirum
